export const groupingMap = [
    {
        label: "Abis Switch Side",
        color: "abis",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                data: "oldAggregSite",
                label: "OLD Aggreg site",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 130
            },
            {
                data: "newAggregSite",
                label: "NEW Aggreg site",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: true,
                manually: true,
                width: 130
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        label: "Primary",
        color: "primary",
        colspan: 0,
        className: "bg-primary",
        columns: [
            {
                data: "region",
                label: "Region",
                type: "dropdown",
                source: ["Casablanca", "Tanger", "Agadir", "Marrackech"],
                mandatory: true,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                data: "name",
                label: "Name",
                type: "text",
                readonly: true,
                mandatory: true,
                manually: false,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                data: "status",
                label: "Status",
                type: "dropdown",
                source: ["Planned", "Implemented", "Archived"],
                allowInvalid: false,
                mandatory: true,
                manually: true,
                width: 110
            },
            {
                data: "archived",
                label: "Archived",
                type: "dropdown",
                source: ["No", "Yes"],
                readOnly: true,
                mandatory: true,
                manually: false,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                data: "vendor",
                label: "Vendor",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                data: "revisionNumber",
                label: "Revision Number",
                type: "numeric",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: false,
                width: 130
            },
            {
                data: "project",
                label: "Project",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        label: "Information",
        color: "info",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                data: "comments",
                label: "Comments",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        label: "Dates",
        color: "dates",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                data: "insertionDate",
                label: "Insertion Date",
                type: "date",
                dateFormat: "DD/MM/YYYY",
                datePickerConfig: {
                    firstDay: 1
                },
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                data: "lastModifiedDate",
                label: "Last Modified Date",
                type: "date",
                dateFormat: "DD/MM/YYYY",
                datePickerConfig: {
                    firstDay: 1
                },
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 140
            },
            {
                data: "archivedDate",
                label: "Archived Date",
                type: "date",
                dateFormat: "DD/MM/YYYY",
                datePickerConfig: {
                    firstDay: 1
                },
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 130
            },
            {
                data: "decommissionDate",
                label: "Decommission",
                type: "date",
                dateFormat: "DD/MM/YYYY",
                datePickerConfig: {
                    firstDay: 1
                },
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 130
            },
            {
                data: "dueDate",
                label: "Due",
                type: "date",
                dateFormat: "DD/MM/YYYY",
                datePickerConfig: {
                    firstDay: 1
                },
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                data: "inServiceDate",
                label: "In Service",
                type: "date",
                dateFormat: "DD/MM/YYYY",
                datePickerConfig: {
                    firstDay: 1
                },
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                data: "installedDate",
                label: "Installed",
                type: "date",
                dateFormat: "DD/MM/YYYY",
                datePickerConfig: {
                    firstDay: 1
                },
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                data: "orderedDate",
                label: "Ordered",
                type: "date",
                dateFormat: "DD/MM/YYYY",
                datePickerConfig: {
                    firstDay: 1
                },
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                data: "scheduledDate",
                label: "Scheduled",
                type: "date",
                dateFormat: "DD/MM/YYYY",
                datePickerConfig: {
                    firstDay: 1
                },
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        label: "Radio Site",
        color: "radio",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                data: "radioSite",
                label: "Radio Site",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: true,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                data: "radioSiteVendor",
                label: "Radio Site Vendor",
                type: "dropdown",
                source: ["ERICSSON ML TN", "Huawei"],
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 130
            },
            {
                data: "accessType",
                label: "Radio Site Access Type",
                type: "dropdown",
                source: ['FE', 'GE'],
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 170
            },
            {
                data: "technology",
                label: "Site Technology",
                type: "dropdown",
                source: ['2G', '2G/3G', '2G/3G/4G', '3G', '3G/4G', '4G'],
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                data: "transmissionScenario",
                label: "Transmission Scenario",
                type: "dropdown",
                source: ['AbisOnly', 'Co-Trans', 'SeparatedTrans'],
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 170
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        label: "Cablage site local MW/RADIO",
        color: "local",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                data: "mwVendor",
                label: "MW Vendor",
                type: "dropdown",
                source: ["ERICSSON", "NEC", "Huawei"],
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                data: "mwEquip",
                label: "MW Equipment",
                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 250
            },
            {
                data: "mwPort",
                label: "MW Port",
                type: "dropdown",
                source: ["Port2 FE", "Port3 FE", "Port4 FE"],
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                data: "foPort",
                label: "FO Port",
                type: "numeric",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        label: "Cablage Site Nodal Agregation MW/IP/OSN",
        color: "nodal",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                data: "preAggregSite",
                label: "PreAggreg site",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                data: "mwPreAggregEquip",
                label: "MW PreAggreg Equip",
                type: 'dropdown',
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                data: "mwPreAggregPort",
                label: "MW PreAggreg Port",
                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                data: "foPreAggregPort",
                label: "FO PreAggreg Port",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                data: "aggregEquipIp",
                label: "Equipment IP",
                type: "dropdown",
                allowInvalid: false,
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                data: "aggregPortIp",
                label: "Port IP",
                type: "dropdown",
                allowInvalid: false,
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                data: "raccordmentOsnA",
                label: "Raccordment OSN A",
                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                data: "raccordmentOsnZ",
                label: "Raccordment OSN Z",
                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        label: "3G Site Side",
        color: "site3g",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                data: "iubVlan",
                label: "3G Iub VLAN",
                type: "numeric",
                validator: "isNumeric",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                data: "iubIp",
                label: "3G Iub IP",
                type: "text",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                data: "iubGw",
                label: "3G IuB GW",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                data: "iubMask",
                label: "3G Iub Mask",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                data: "omVlan",
                label: "3G O&M VLAN",
                validator: "isNumeric",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                data: "omIp",
                label: "3G O&M IP",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                data: "omGw",
                label: "3G O&M GW",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                data: "omMask",
                label: "3G O&M Mask",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        label: "4G Site Side",
        color: "site4g",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                data: "s1cp_x2cpVlan",
                label: "4G S1-CP & X2-CP VLAN",
                validator: "isNumeric",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 170
            },
            {
                data: "s1cp_x2cpIp",
                label: "4G S1-CP & X2-CP IP",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 170
            },
            {
                data: "s1cp_x2cpGw",
                label: "4G S1-CP & X2-CP GW",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 170
            },
            {
                data: "s1cp_x2cpMask",
                label: "4G S1-CP & X2-CP Mask",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 170
            },
            {
                data: "s1up_x2upVlan",
                label: "4G S1-UP & X2-UP VLAN",
                validator: "isNumeric",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 170
            },
            {
                data: "s1up_x2upIp",
                label: "4G S1-UP & X2-UP IP",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 170
            },
            {
                data: "s1up_x2upGw",
                label: "4G S1-UP & X2-UP GW",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 170
            },
            {
                data: "s1up_x2upMask",
                label: "4G S1-UP & X2-UP Mask",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 170
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        label: "BSC Side",
        color: "bsc",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                data: "bsc",
                label: "BSC",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: false,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                data: "bscBoardName",
                label: "BSC Board Name",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: true,
                manually: true,
                width: 130
            },
            {
                data: "bscIp",
                label: "BSC IP",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 110
            },
            {
                data: "bscNextHopIp",
                label: "Next Hope BSC",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 130
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        label: "3G RNC Side",
        color: "rnc",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {

                manually: true,
                width: 100

            {

    {
        label: "2G Site Side",
        color: "site2g",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                data: "btsGtmuVersion",

            {
                data: "btsIp",
